  },
  "*** We're almost there! Hold for 30 seconds and we're safe! ***": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
      "JP": "*** もうすぐだ！ 30秒間持ちこたえれば、安全だ！ ***",
